dct_title_s: A map of the Britisch [sic] Empire in America with the French, Spanish and the Dutch settlements adjacent thereto
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Prevailing wind directions in the lower latitudes are also shown. Includes illustrations, inset views and detail maps.
dct_publisher_sm: London : Grave par Jean Conr. Back, 1756.
